      <div class="row userInfo">

        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12">

          <h1 class="title-big text-center section-title-style2">
              <span> Contact us </span>
          </h1>

          <p class="lead text-center">
              We stand behind every Northside product we make. If you have any questions or concerns regarding a Northside purchase, please contact our customer service team. We want to ensure the most positive experience possible when you shop Northside, and we are committed to meeting your needs as best we can.
          </p>

